## SatoshiSploder

[Satoshi Sploder](http://www.satoshisploder.com/)

The satoshi sploder is a quick lottery system. Players add bitcoins to a pool to increase their chances of winning other players bitcoins in the pool.


#### Winning Chances

* Chances of winning are equal to the percentage of your bitcoins contribute to the pot.

* See Details on Website

#### Payout

* Instant Payout


